{"tid":1403802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3/8黃大仙劇本及真實起因","createTime":"2019-08-03T22:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T23:19:38.000Z","uid":58841,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"af42f95cc3b6438249b3cedfb2ccd234c7e4cfbc","tid":1403802,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T22:53:26.000Z","msg":"睇左幾個post同收返黎既一手料<br />\n黑警原來劇本：<br />\n1. 混入示威者人群，以快閃名義從九龍城引佢地去黃大仙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7eAjDN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7eAjDN.png&h=66dd2fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 同一時間，黑警已經通知左商場內部做野<br />\n[陰謀論]懷疑警犬預知今晚黃大仙衝突<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n3. 黑警準備係黃大仙佈防，然後由<span style=\"color: blue;\">黃</span>大仙街坊帶風向<br />\n4.一網打盡，CCTVB臥底再利用旺角單野黎個反cup<br />\n<br />\n事實上：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span>大仙街坊見到下面好多狗，衝落去散步撚狗<br />\n2. 前線手足去到快閃狗屋發現唔對路無理隻鬼<br />\n3. 狗舍住客失控高空擲物<br />\n4. 其他媒體唔知發生咩事，但偏偏得CCTVB知<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母垃圾CCTVB<br />\n一陣你同我睇住黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將軍澳撚已經憎你地憎到仆街"},{"pid":"2f33afcbce430cbfc9c3559948d2c6d5c77c2ca1","tid":1403802,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T23:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f40fede4db3184b28c2bd4d461c28ee0d2a46da8","tid":1403802,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T23:19:38.000Z","msg":"漏左連登：<br />\n分化撚透過屌前線黎分化和理非同前線，如果加埋原來劇本事半功倍<br />\n<br />\n事實上：<br />\n黃大仙顯靈，focus哂去勇武街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}